{
  "texts": [
    "To investigate this, students' complete learning logs from a semester are used to forecast their course performance (Pass/Withdrawn or Pass/Fail).For the binary classification problems of Pass/Fail and Pass/Withdrawn, only samples from the relevant classes were used.",
    "The experiment encompasses two distinct sub-tasks.",
    "The first task involves categorizing students into two groups: Pass or Fail, based on their risk of failing.",
    "The second task focuses on classifying students into Pass or Withdrawn, depending on their risk of discontinuing their studies.",
    "Table 4 presents the experimental results for the tasks."
  ]
}